sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant UI as /preflight client
  participant Orchestrator as executeRunPlan
  participant Adapter as Sandpack adapter
  participant Iframe as Cross-origin iframe

  User->>UI: Run planned states
  UI->>Orchestrator: validated RunPlan + retained source + AbortSignal
  loop Each fixture in RunPlan order
    Orchestrator->>Adapter: executeFixture(sessionId, runId, fixture)
    Adapter->>Iframe: fresh react-ts virtual project
    Iframe-->>Adapter: correlated runtime event
    Adapter->>Adapter: validate marker, nonce, IDs, type and source window
    Iframe-->>Adapter: active Sandpack completion or diagnostic
    Adapter-->>Orchestrator: schema-valid fixture result
    Adapter->>Iframe: cleanup active lifecycle
    Orchestrator-->>UI: ordered progress
  end
  Orchestrator-->>UI: validated completed or cancelled session
